description: Starting with the finest ingredients around, DeMarco's Italian Ice is making a dessert that's sure to have you coming back for more! There's nothing quite like the taste of all natural, handcrafted Italian ice, especially when it's made from scratch by people who are truly dedicated to making the most amazing frozen treats on the Phoenix streets. From the Citrus Swirl to the Spumoni to the Pistachio and more, DeMarco's is bringing you nothing but the very best!
name: DeMarco Italian Ice
